headline: This carbon fiber stock is a major contributor to defense sector
summary: Gabelli Funds Portfolio Manager Tony Bancroft — who oversees the Gabelli Commercial Aerospace and Defense ETF (GCAD) — discusses the broader defense sector and names one of his top defense stocks. Also hear Tony Bancroft's latest analysis on Boeing's (BA) third quarter revenue print, free cash flow figures, and wider-than-expected loss. headline: RTX (RTX): Assessing Valuation Following Strong Q3 Results, Upbeat Outlook, and Dividend Announcement
summary: RTX delivered third-quarter results that topped expectations and lifted its full-year forecast, while also declaring another quarterly dividend.
